official_title: SpotCheck: Comparison of Enhanced Telemedicine Versus In-person Evaluation for the Diagnosis of Skin Cancer
inclusion_criteria:
* Be 18 years of age or older
* Have 1-3 lesions for evaluation
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
Must have maximum age of 90 Years
exclusion_criteria: * Lesions of the hair-bearing scalp, in the mouth, on the lips, genitalia, nails, on/around the eyes, inside the ear
